Package net.ohdm

Class LineString

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.ohdm.LineString
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Polygon
    public class LineString
extends java.lang.Object
    The LineString class represents path between Points. A LineString consists of an ordered series of Points. The first Point in a LineString is called Head The last Point in a LineString is called Tail
    Author:
    Meron Nagy
